{"tid":2291330,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"低齡戀不是罪 Dear Joe Biden, We support you from Hong Kong.","createTime":"2020-11-18T16:21:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-19T12:51:43.000Z","uid":169112,"like":6,"dislike":29,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"25cc6abc498f3133ff6ed9113175d4b83e078886","tid":2291330,"uid":169112,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T16:21:01.000Z","msg":"＃立即釋放龍緯汶  <br />\n#香港首位性小眾平權犧牲者￼<br />\n#拜登無罪<br />\n<br />\n早前我們爭取「人骸戀」平權及除罪化，更拍下首位出櫃的香港人骸戀者「阿屍」的剖白片段，我們也是首個香港團體反對政府把「姦屍罪」立法。<br />\n<br />\n今天，我們再看到另一個性小眾群體被打壓－－低齡戀。<br />\n<br />\n像同性戀一樣，低齡戀一直被社會視為禁忌、嘔心及精神病。大眾常以「戀童癖」一詞污名化他們，認為高低齡人士之間沒有戀愛和性愛的權利。然而，何謂兒童？有些文化認為六十歲仍是青年；有些文化認為6-8歲已是成年，會為他們舉行成人禮。兒童的分類根本是社會建構的文化產物，用以穩固「成年人」打壓低齡人士性愛自由的霸權工具，稱他們沒有足夠心智能力作出自願性行為。即使龍緯汶 跟六歲女性是兩情相悅，也不獲法庭受理。￼￼這些偏見導致社會長期忽略低齡戀者的情慾需要，踐踏他們人性尊嚴。<br />\n<br />\n我們相信愛沒有性別、生死和年齡之分，愛就是愛。若然一個女「童」跟龍緯汶或拜登真心相愛，自願性交，這又傷害了誰呢？為何你情我願的事情，需要法院管制？需要被視為美國大選的醜聞？需要他人指手畫腳？這不是一種赤裸裸對性小眾的壓迫又是甚麼呢？<br />\n<br />\n根據香港法律，無論兒童是否同意被告向他 / 她作出嚴重猥褻的行為，或是否同意應被告的邀請，向被告作出嚴重猥褻的行為，都不重要。只要涉及的行為被認定是嚴重猥褻，而涉及的兒童不足16歲，被告就會被裁定罪名成立。<br />\n這惡法明顯歧視低齡戀人士。應立即廢除！<br />\n<br />\n讓我們對低齡戀性小眾：多一點包容，少一點歧視！<br />\n<br />\nDear Joe Biden,<br />\nWe support you from Hong Kong.<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg4-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/fr/cp0/e15/q65/126007694_3481006891989452_3269233553052915491_o.jpg?_nc_cat=110&amp;ccb=2&amp;_nc_sid=8024bb&amp;_nc_ohc=xPy7GBq9eoQAX_37qch&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg4-1.fna&amp;tp=14&amp;oh=25f657e54abd226e2147ce33d093a134&amp;oe=5FDA7127\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg4-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2Ffr%2Fcp0%2Fe15%2Fq65%2F126007694_3481006891989452_3269233553052915491_o.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D110%26ccb%3D2%26_nc_sid%3D8024bb%26_nc_ohc%3DxPy7GBq9eoQAX_37qch%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg4-1.fna%26tp%3D14%26oh%3D25f657e54abd226e2147ce33d093a134%26oe%3D5FDA7127&h=b23b623a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n原Link<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/HKCorrectness/photos/a.1282790118477818/3481006878656120/?type=3&amp;source=48&amp;__tn__=EH-R\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2FHKCorrectness%2Fphotos%2Fa.1282790118477818%2F3481006878656120%2F%3Ftype%3D3%26source%3D48%26__tn__%3DEH-R&d=VbAd486K8RrC2DEUtq3b5skuRvkIHaPazTq7BlmTy1I%3D&h=e5060fce\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/HKCorrectness/photos/a.1282790118477818/3481006878656120/?type=3&amp;source=48&amp;__tn__=EH-R</a>"},{"pid":"8e67dd37cd303f344ac6f97b2921bc2b8aa57817","tid":2291330,"uid":253170,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T16:22:11.000Z","msg":"童性戀無罪！"},{"pid":"2d1758ee17bc70070732244b947c5a41886207d4","tid":2291330,"uid":169112,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T16:23:01.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"79a0eeea39b684f3328391d4e2147412f129cd93","tid":2291330,"uid":169112,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T16:23:43.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"0e577e919e3ae3e668b1df8b65b5b96d97437c5b","tid":2291330,"uid":169112,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T16:25:33.000Z","msg":"3"},{"pid":"43103ff5917d47be1d0c4658125a508cdc2b440b","tid":2291330,"uid":334292,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T16:26:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />又好似有啲道理咁喎"},{"pid":"2674dce1819dc01ac43f34fe27878bd22c9f9e9c","tid":2291330,"uid":62650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8e67dd37cd303f344ac6f97b2921bc2b8aa57817","tid":2291330,"uid":253170,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T16:22:11.000Z","msg":"童性戀無罪！"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T16:49:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9cc24a21ed025c03905037b0caa32d132aa21009","tid":2291330,"uid